OL,7,FThe cause of deaths of hundreds of
OL,8,Flearning disabled people were recorded
OL,9,Fincorrectly by an NHS and government-
OL,10,Fbacked review, leading to the number
OL,11,Fof avoidable deaths being
OL,12,Funderreported.
OL,14,FCampaigners say it is "deeply
OL,15,Fworrying" and "disrespectful" that the
OL,16,Fofficial report was published with
OL,17,Fsuch "significant" errors, after
OL,18,Finitially being delayed for almost a
OL,19,Fyear.
