OL,7,FThe Learning from Lives and Deaths of
OL,8,FPeople with a Learning Disability and
OL,9,FAutistic People (LeDeR) is an annual
OL,10,FNHS-funded review which examines the
OL,11,Fdeaths of learning disabled and
OL,12,Fautistic people, to address why so
OL,13,Fmany are dying prematurely and with
OL,14,Ftreatable health conditions.
OL,16,FThe latest report, which records
OL,17,Fdeaths from 2023, has been mired in
OL,18,Fscandal. It was meant to be published
OL,19,Fin 2024, but was delayed by almost a
OL,20,Fyear and not released until September
OL,21,F2025 due to data issues.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
