OL,3,CBereaved families 'disrespected' as
OL,4,Clearning disabled deaths recorded in
OL,5,Cerror
OL,7,FThen, in December, the report had to
OL,8,Fbe withdrawn entirely over what NHS
OL,9,FEngland called a "technical issue",
OL,10,Fafter hundreds of causes of death were
OL,11,Fsubmitted incorrectly.
OL,13,FThe 2023 report has now been re-
OL,14,Fpublished, in January 2026, with the
OL,15,Fauthors of the report from King's
OL,16,FCollege London "satisfied this data is
OL,17,Fnow accurate."
