OL,7,FThe new LeDeR has found that the
OL,8,Finitial review understated the number
OL,9,Fof learning disabled people whose
OL,10,Fdeaths were avoidable, rising from
OL,11,F38.8% to 40.2%. This is double the
OL,12,Famount of avoidable deaths compared to
OL,13,Fthe general population.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
