OL,7,F"It's deeply worrying the 2023 report
OL,8,Fwas significantly delayed, then
OL,9,Fpublished with serious errors and
OL,10,Fwithdrawn. We now know around 300
OL,11,Freviews into deaths were reported
OL,12,Fincorrectly, leading to changes in the
OL,13,Fannual report's England-wide findings
OL,14,Fon causes of death and avoidable
OL,15,Fdeaths. This is deeply upsetting for
OL,16,Ffamilies impacted and must not happen
OL,17,Fagain.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
