OL,7,FProfessor Sara Ryan, who specialises
OL,8,Fin learning disability care and whose
OL,9,Flearning disabled son Connor died
OL,10,Favoidably in 2013, argues the LeDeR
OL,11,Freview needs to be replaced.
OL,13,F"Is anyone going to ask why the review
OL,14,Fwas delayed for nearly a year for data
OL,15,Fquality checking, and they missed a
OL,16,Fflawed process?" she said.
