OL,7,F"This report really reads as a mess,
OL,8,Fhurriedly revised to be just as much
OL,9,Fof a mess...a hefty dose of disrespect
OL,10,Ffor people who died prematurely and
OL,11,Ftheir families."
OL,13,FResponding to the latest publication,
OL,14,FCare Minister Dr Zubir Ahmed issued no
OL,15,Fapology to in a written statement in
OL,16,Fthe House of Commons, but acknowledged
OL,17,F"how concerning the retraction will
OL,18,Fhave been for bereaved families and
OL,19,Fstakeholders who place great trust in
OL,20,Fthe LeDeR process."
