OL,12,FLord Scriven, whose nephew Myles had a
OL,13,Flearning disability and died in 2023
OL,14,Fdue to neglectful care at an NHS
OL,15,Fhospital, says an overhaul is needed
OL,16,Fof how deaths are recorded.
OL,18,F"The saga of this report is nothing
OL,19,Fshort of a national scandal," he told
OL,20,FITV News.
