OL,7,F"To have families wait nearly two
OL,8,Fyears for data on the deaths of their
OL,9,Floved ones, only to be presented with
OL,10,Fa document so riddled with technical
OL,11,Ferrors that it had to be retracted, is
OL,12,Fa slap in the face to every person
OL,13,Fwith a learning disability in this
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
