OL,3,CBereaved families 'disrespected' as
OL,4,Clearning disabled deaths recorded in
OL,5,Cerror
OL,7,F"These aren't just 'data points' or
OL,8,F'automated defects'`they are human
OL,9,Flives. My own nephew, Myles, was one
OL,10,Fof those lives. Behind every corrected
OL,11,Fstatistic in this January update is a
OL,12,Ffamily who has been left in limbo by a
OL,13,Fbureaucratic machine that seems more
OL,14,Finterested in managing its own image
OL,15,Fthan in preventing premature deaths.
OL,17,F"If the NHS cannot even count these
OL,18,Fdeaths accurately, how on earth can we
OL,19,Ftrust them to stop them?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
