OL,3,CBereaved families 'disrespected' as
OL,4,Clearning disabled deaths recorded in
OL,5,Cerror
OL,7,F"I am calling for an urgent overhaul
OL,8,Fof this flawed process and a move to
OL,9,Fan enforceable, statutory systems that
OL,10,Fhold Integrated Care Boards to
OL,11,Faccount. We don't need more 'robust
OL,12,Fdata checking protocols'; we need a
OL,13,Fsystem that treats the deaths of
OL,14,Flearning-disabled people with the same
OL,15,Furgency as any other national health
OL,16,Fcrisis."
